high_descs: Walk towards the sofa then turn left face the center table
Pick up the remote on the table beside the book
Turn to your right and head towards the lamp
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the remote by the light

high_descs: Cross the room and turn left and then turn to face the table with the remote.
Pick up the remote from the table.
Go right and then turn right again to face the lamp with the pink stand.
Turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a remote in hand.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left to face the coffee table with your back to the couch.
Pick up the remote from the table.
Turn right and go to the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Use lamp light to look at the remote.

high_descs: Move to the wooden coffee table facing the remote
Pick up the remote on top of the table
Carry the remote to the floor lamp in the corner of the room
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry a remote while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Walk to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote.
Go to the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at the remote by lamp light.

high_descs: go to the end of the floor rug and turn to the left and go to the middle of the coffee table and turn to the left
pick up the remote control from the coffee table
turn to the right and go to the end of the floor rug and turn to the right and take a step and turn left and go to the wall and turn right and go to the floor lamp
turn on the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the light of a lamp
